@startuml CoreNeedleBiopsy_Workflow_RejectedSpecimen
title Szenario 2: Probenabweisung\nCore Needle Biopsy – Unzureichendes Material

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #555555
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #555555
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #AAAAAA
skinparam sequenceGroupFontSize 11
skinparam noteFontSize 10
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8DC

participant "**Placer (KIS)**\nUrologie" as Placer #BDD7EE
participant "**Filler (LIS)**\nPathologie" as Filler #C6EFCE

== Auftragserstellung (2024-01-15, 08:00) ==

Placer -> Filler : POST Bundle (type: **transaction**)\n  Patient\n  ServiceRequest (status: **active**)\n  Specimen [x12] (status: **available**)\n  Task (status: **requested**, code: fulfill)
activate Filler
Filler --> Placer : Bundle (type: **transaction-response**)\n  201 Created
deactivate Filler

note over Placer, Filler : **Task V1: requested**

== Probenempfang & Annahme (2024-01-15, 14:00) ==

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task\n(status: **accepted**)
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 200 OK
deactivate Placer

note over Placer, Filler : **Task V2: accepted**

== Bearbeitung beginnt (2024-01-16, 08:00) ==

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task\n(status: **in-progress**)
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 200 OK
deactivate Placer

note over Placer, Filler : **Task V3: in-progress**

== Probenabweisung (2024-01-16, 09:00) ==

Filler -> Filler : Makroskopie:\nStanze 05 enthaelt\nkein verwertbares Gewebe\n(nur Blut/Fett)

Filler -> Placer : PUT Specimen[05]\n(status: **unsatisfactory**\ncondition: insufficient)
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 200 OK
deactivate Placer

Filler -> Placer : PUT Task\n(status: **failed**\nstatusReason: "Specimen 05\nunzureichendes Material"\noutput: Specimen[05])
activate Placer
Placer --> Filler : 200 OK
deactivate Placer

note over Placer, Filler #FFD7D7 : **Task V4: failed**\nKein DiagnosticReport erstellt\nSpecimen.status: unsatisfactory\nSpecimen.condition: insufficient

== Reaktion des Placers ==

Placer -> Placer : ServiceRequest\n(status: **ended**)

note over Placer : Kein Befund moeglich.\nOption: Erneute Biopsie\nplanen (neues Szenario 1).

@enduml
